quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,71,"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko jillaŇčton goonga kan e meh-re nden ho…óon cuu…óa goonga kan tara onon ho…óon ganndi?"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e yim…ďe Defte …ďen wi'i: "Gom…óinee ko jippinaa kon e …ďen gom…óim…ďe ka arannde √Īallal, yeddon ka sakkitoode mayre, bela jo'o, …ďe ruttoo."
  3,73,"Wato on gom…óin si wonaa on jokku…óo diina mon kan". Maaku: "Pellet, ko Peewal Alla ngal woni Peewal". [Ko kulil fii ] wata go…ó…óo goo okke yeu ko okka…óon kon maa …ďe wennjiroya on …óum ko Joomi mon. Maaku: "Pellet …ďural ngal ko e Junngo Alla woni, Homo wee…óa ngal on Mo O Muuyi". Alla ko jaac…óo […ďural] Anndu…óo."
  3,74,"Hombo Hertinana Yurmeende Makko nde on mo o muuyi. Alla ko Jom …ďuural Mawngal."
  3,75,"No e yim…ďe Defte …ďen, on mo kalfiŇčtaa jawdi wonayndi KINTAAR, on jonnite ndi; hino e ma…ď…ďe kadi, on mo kalfiŇčtaa "diinaaru", on jonnitataa ma ndu si wanaa a darani mo daŇčkaranni-…óaa. ∆äum non, ko tawde kam…ďe …ďe wi'i: "Laatanaaki men e humammbinnee…ďe …ďen laawol"; hi…ďe ta∆īa penaale huma e Alla hara kam…ďe he…ďe nganndi."
  3,76,"Aa'a, kala kuu6nu…óo ahadi mu'un o huli, pellet, Alla no Yi…ói huloo…ďe Mo …ďen."
  3,77,"∆Āen wostorat…ďe ahadi Alla ndin e goondooje ma…ď…ďe coggeloy pam…óukoy, …ďen …óon, ge…ďal alanaa …ďe ka laakara, Alla yeewtidataa e ma…ď…ďe, O Ndaaroytaa …ďe √Ďande Darngal, O La…ď…ďiŇčtaa …ďe, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe."